data.description: Picture a charming ranch-style home nestled in a thriving community. This inviting home boasts four cozy bedrooms, providing ample space for a growing family or hosting guests. With two well-appointed bathrooms, mornings and evenings are a breeze for everyone! Located within walking distance of growing Oswego, convenience becomes a way of life. You can easily stroll to local shops, cafes, or community events. The sizable yard offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities, whether it's hosting barbecues, creating a garden retreat, or simply enjoying some peaceful relaxation. Minutes to excellent Oswego schools, shops, restaurants and the riverfront! Come see this home before it is gone!
